ZH: 我的喉咙发炎了，我需要去看医生。
EN: My throat is inflamed, I need to see a doctor.

ZH: 如果你的伤口发炎，要及时处理。
EN: If your wound becomes inflamed, you should treat it promptly.

ZH: 她的眼睛发炎，所以不方便看书。
EN: Her eyes are inflamed, so she cannot read.

ZH: 我的脚趾发炎了，穿鞋很痛苦。
EN: My toe is inflamed, wearing shoes is very painful.

ZH: 这种药可以用来治疗发炎。
EN: This medicine can be used to treat inflammation.

ZH: 他的喉咙发炎得去医院开点药。
EN: His throat is inflamed, he has to go to the hospital to get some medicine.

ZH: 他的发炎情况越来越严重了。
EN: His inflammation is getting worse.

ZH: 感冒发炎时要多喝水，多休息。
EN: When you have a cold with inflammation, drink more water and get more rest.

ZH: 手指受伤发炎了，用点药吧。
EN: The finger is injured and inflamed, apply some medicine.

ZH: 头发床榻有发炎反应吗？
EN: Does the hair follicle have any inflammation reaction?

ZH: 发炎的伤口可能会感染。
EN: An inflamed wound may become infected.

ZH: 腹部肌肉发炎的症状是什么？
EN: What are the symptoms of abdominal muscle inflammation?

ZH: 某些食物容易引起人体内部发炎。
EN: Some foods can easily cause inflammation in the body.

ZH: 运动后如果感到发炎疼痛，要及时行医。
EN: If you feel inflamed and painful after exercise, seek medical attention promptly.

ZH: 这种草药可以降低发炎的症状。
EN: This herb can reduce the symptoms of inflammation.

ZH: 皮肤发炎需要及时擦药和保持清洁。
EN: Inflamed skin needs to be treated with ointment and kept clean promptly.

ZH: 发炎是人体对外来刺激的一种自然反应。
EN: Inflammation is a natural response of the body to external stimuli.

ZH: 酒精和辣椒会导致腹部发炎。
EN: Alcohol and chili peppers can cause inflammation in the abdomen.

ZH: 感染引起的发炎需要使用抗生素治疗。
EN: Inflammation caused by infection needs to be treated with antibiotics.

ZH: 他的肺部发炎，需要住院治疗。
EN: His lungs are inflamed and he needs to be hospitalized for treatment.
